data.description: You don't want to miss out on this all brick ranch style home in the estate section of the coveted Doe Valley subdivision! The main floor offers an open living/dining area, a natural gas fireplace, 2 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths, and convenient main floor laundry. One of the main floor bedrooms could be considered a primary bedroom, it features a private full bathroom. Downstairs, you'll find a secondary master suite with a large walk in closet and full bathroom. This home is one of just TWO homes on this cul-de-sac and is just minutes from Doe Valley's Swim and Tennis Club, pool, lake with beach access, tennis courts, and basketball court. Don't wait to schedule your tour, call today!
